'''''J.R.R. Tolkien: the Man and His Myth''''' is a four-volume box set published in [[1978]] containing ''[[A Guide to Middle-earth]]'' (first edition) by [[Robert Foster]], ''[[Master of Middle-earth]]'' by [[Paul H. Kocher]], ''[[Tolkien: A Look Behind The Lord of the Rings]]'' by [[Lin Carter]], and [[J.R.R. Tolkien: A Biography]] by [[Humphrey Carpenter]].<ref>{{webcite|author=|articleurl=https://www.tolkienbooks.us/slipcases/othersc/j-r-r-tolkien-the-man-and-his-myth-1978|articlename=J.R.R. Tolkien: The Man & His Myth (1978)|website=TolkienBooks.US|accessed=9 September 2021}}</ref>

